1. Install profile
git clone https://github.com/RononDex/archdotfiles
sh profile-enabler.sh

2. zsh
install zsh
install zsh-completions
chsh -s full-path-to-shell
install oh-my-zsh
sh -c "$(wget https://raw.github.com/robbyrussell/oh-my-zsh/master/tools/install.sh -O -)"

3. Network manager
pacman -S networkmanager
systemctl enable NetworkManager
pacman -S gnome-keyring (for wifi wpa keyring)
pacman -S network-manager-applet

4. Window manager
i3-gaps
adobe-source-code-pro-fonts (Use as console font)
https://aur.archlinux.org/ttf-material-icons.git (AUR)
polybar
lxterminal
xsession
light-git (AUR)
flameshot (AUR)
compton
arc-gtk theme (AUR)
lxappearance
nerd-fonts-complete (AUR)
...

5. Sound
install pulseaudio
install alsa
install pulseaudio-alsa
install pulseaudio-jack
install pulseaudio-bluetooth
install pavucontrol (audio control gdk)

5. Display manager
lightdm
webkit greeter
litarvan (theme)

5. lock screen
light-locker

6. bluetooth
install bluez
install bluez-utils
systemctl enable bluetooth
systemctl start bluetooth
install blueman (GDK bluetooth interface)

7. Other stuff
nautilus
autofs, cifs
samba
vlc

7. Steam
Install Steam
Install Steam-fonts (AUR)
